Betty Johnson of Missouri was a Kansas City Chiefs season ticket holder since 1986 . 
  She was a great-great grandmother and lost her home to pay for her season tickets . 
  On Thursday, Chiefs Hall of Famer Nick Lowery visited Johnson and she passed away shortly after . 
  She had said goodbye to everyone except her team . 
  Johnson was a devoted fan and received a kiss from Dwayne Bowe every game . 
 